all-packages.description:
			The &lt;b&gt;ANSI&lt;/b&gt; library.&lt;br&gt;
			&lt;br&gt;
			A basic library to encode strings with ANSI escape codes
            to provide colors output in the terminal (Linux and Mac OS X).
			&lt;br&gt;
			&lt;br&gt;
			&lt;b&gt;Windows is not supported yet.&lt;/b&gt;
			&lt;br&gt;
			&lt;br&gt;
			&lt;a href="https://github.com/Corsaair/ansilib/wiki" target="_blank"&gt;Wiki Documentation&lt;/a&gt;
